gpRepel
====

Currently, only Linux install is supported for gpRepel. Here are the 
Linux installation steps:

1) Install NVIDIA CUDA Toolkit on your Linux system. Instruction for 
   Fedora Linux can be found at:

     http://www.r-tutor.com/gpu-computing/cuda-installation
     
2) Export the following environment variable in .bashrc:

     export R_LIBS_USER="<path of some folder in your home directory>"

3) Then enter the following:

     R CMD INSTALL gpRepel_<version>.tar.gz
     
     
